==In-Game Content News==

===Kai Ni Remodels===
By this "Main Summer", there will be two new Kai Ni remodels released.
*{{ShipLink|Yura}} Kai Ni
**It has been announced in the Zuiun Festival Live Event in Fuji-Q Highland that her Kai Ni Remodel update is quite close.
***Received through [[Thread:567463|June 23rd Update]].
*Large Aircraft Carrier Second Remodel
**{{ShipLink|Saratoga}} had been previously hinted for Kai Ni release back in December 2016 via KanColle Style Vol.3 Magazine interview.[http://kancolle.doorblog.jp/archives/50216019.html]
**The Zuiun Festival Live Event in Fuji-Q Highland has confirmed the Kai Ni Remodel is for a Large Foreign Aircraft Carrier.[http://kancolle.doorblog.jp/archives/51518014.html]
***By displacement amongst currently existing Foreign Aircraft Carriers, {{ShipLink|Saratoga}} has the largest displacement.[https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_aircraft_carriers_of_World_War_II]
**Confirmed to be {{ShipLink|Saratoga}} via [[Thread:569593|May 2017 Ranking Rewards]], with Developers stating the Equipment from the Ranking Rewards will be available in the incoming update via a Kai-2 Remodel and Improvements from [[Akashi's Improvement Arsenal]].[http://i.imgur.com/0VSkTVv.jpg]

===Yukata Seasonal CGs===
*Starting from this Summer this year, there will be several Yukata Seasonal limited-time CGs given out to many ship girls.
**There will be content to have the player be able to decorate the Naval Base into a major Summer festival-like environment.

===Other In-Game Contents===
*This year several in-game UI will be going through major redesigns and upgrades.
*Etorofu's artist, Akasaka Yuzu had previously designed the Wall Scroll furnitures before.

===Other News===
*Uchida Shuu, the voice actor for {{ShipLink|Warspite}}, has announced that she will be designated to voice a new ship scheduled for release in the future.
**Unconfirmed if it is another Royal Navy Ship however.

